               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar “Synaxarion” for the first half of the year (fols.
                     3ra-299rb)
 I-1) Maskaram (fols. 3ra–57vc)
 I-2) Ṭǝqǝmt (fols.
                     58ra–101rc)
 I-3) Ḫǝdār (fols. 101va–149vc)
 I-4) Tāḫśāś (fols.
                     150ra–202vc)
 I-5) Ṭǝrr (fols. 203ra–260vb)
 I-6) Yakkātit (fols.
                     260va–299rb)
 The commemorative notices are followed by ʿarke-hymns
                     
 Additiones 1-2; colophon.</summary>
